Package: pbiasr
Type: Package
Title: Publication Bias Testing for Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.2.7
Authors@R: person(given = "OpenAI", family = "Assistant", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: Runs a unified set of publication-bias tests for meta-analysis and returns
    raw machine-readable publication-bias results together with a formatted display
    table. Results are classified into the paper's size-by-I-squared cases and
    sorted by the corresponding Balanced Accuracy ranking. Estimated effects
    and model-parameter estimates are intentionally not reported. The main
    interface requires only effect sizes and their standard errors. Methods that
    additionally need study-level sample size proxies can use the optional 'obs'
    argument.
